<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>dinoblog</title>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>dinoblog</h1>
  </header>
  <main>
    <h2>Success!</h2>
    <p>Your blog as been created and can be viewed <a href="http://<%= subdomain %>.dinoblog.net">here</a>!</p>

    <p>The password to edit your content is '<%= password %>'. <b>Don't lose it!</b></p>

    <p>Your site content can be updated at this URL: <a href="<%= subdomain %>/_edit"><%= subdomain %>.dinoblog.net/_edit</a>. To edit a blog post, simply navigate to the post you wish to edit and append '/_edit' to the URL.</p>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
